Conclusion: CD 2 better fulfils my core priorities—analog warmth, wide dynamics, minimal compression, immersive imaging, long‑form sequencing that rewards collector‑style, uninterrupted listens—so I choose CD 2 and reject CD 1 for being more concise and track‑focused than I prefer.

